These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, accountant
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, american
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike
1. the accountant is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the software-developer is on the right of the accountant##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | tea      | water    |
| Job           | accountant | software-developer |
| Nationality   | egyptian       | american  |
| Transport     | taxi      | motorbike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, pear
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, classical
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, motorbike
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
2. the person eating pear is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | pear | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | classical         |
| Pet           | snake     | hedgehog         |
| Transport     | motorbike    | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, chess
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, fisherman
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, disco
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, skateboard
1. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | chess          | traveling |
| Job           | fisherman | nurse     |
| Music-Genre   | d&b            | disco         |
| Transport     | skateboard         | trike   |

 #################################

 
