.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, grapes
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, punk
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of rock is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | tea |
| Food          | grapes   | watermelon |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | rock     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | helicopter     |

 